    wordSentence: {title:"词句段运用",titleEn:"Word & Sentence Practice",content:{cn:"读下面的诗句，联系你读过的古诗，说说有哪些事物在诗中被赋予了人的品格和志向。\n◇千磨万击还坚劲，任尔东西南北风。\n◇不要人夸好颜色，只留清气满乾坤。\n◇荷尽已无擎雨盖，菊残犹有傲霜枝。",en:"Read the poem lines and discuss: what objects are given human qualities and aspirations?\nAlso consider how descriptions of appearance and manner contribute to characterization."}},
    accumulation: {title:"日积月累",titleEn:"Accumulation",content:{cn:"有意栽花花不发，无心插柳柳成荫。\n良药苦口利于病，忠言逆耳利于行。\n树欲静而风不止，子欲养而亲不待。\n常将有日思无日，莫把无时当有时。\n书到用时方恨少，事非经过不知难。",en:"Planting flowers with care, they may not bloom; a casually planted willow grows into shade.\nBitter medicine benefits the illness; honest advice is hard to hear but benefits conduct.\nThe tree wants calm but the wind won't stop; a child wants to care for parents but they won't wait.\nIn times of plenty, think of scarcity; when you have time, don't treat it as limitless.\nYou regret not reading enough when knowledge is needed; you don't know how hard something is until you've done it."}}
