        en: "Before graduation, carry out activities to bring a perfect conclusion to primary school life.\n\n1. Hold a farewell party — express feelings of parting through performances.\n2. Write letters — write to teachers or classmates recalling good times; write to your school with sincere suggestions; write to your future self with dreams and hopes."
